\uc3 \u8221\'e2\'80\'9d is a new scientist\u8217\'e2\'80\'99s struggle to come to terms with the relationship of the individual to the species, the entry to the collection, the self to the community, and the theory to the preceding body of knowledge. These categories bleed into each other for Darwin, culminating in an essentially social inference that carves out the theoretical space where Darwin\u8217\'e2\'80\'99s eventual legacy will develop.\uc1 }
